562
00:40:34,225 --> 00:40:38,465
"Dear leaders, colleagues,
this is He Yuanhang."

563
00:40:38,545 --> 00:40:41,105
<i>As a recognized contributor</i>
<i>to the June 30 case,</i>

564
00:40:41,625 --> 00:40:44,865
<i>I have a duty to report the findings</i>

565
00:40:44,945 --> 00:40:46,985
<i>of the reinvestigation as follows…</i>

566
00:40:48,745 --> 00:40:51,265
He already wrote a report.

567
00:40:51,345 --> 00:40:52,865
Why keep investigating?

568
00:40:53,905 --> 00:40:55,185
He lost his memory.

569
00:40:56,185 --> 00:40:57,305
What do you know?

570
00:40:57,385 --> 00:40:58,505
This must have been written
by Captain Ran.

571
00:40:58,585 --> 00:41:01,065
He didn't want to affect
He Yuanhang's merit award,

572
00:41:01,145 --> 00:41:04,305
so he put the credit on He Yuanhang.

